sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Browser
    participant FLB as Fast Lazy Bee
    participant PS as Pub/Sub
    participant EP as event-processor
    participant FS as Firestore
    participant GW as websocket-gateway

    Client->>FLB: GET /api/v1/movies/:id
    FLB-->>Client: 200 OK (movie data)
    FLB-)PS: publish movie_viewed event

    PS-)EP: trigger
    EP->>FS: upsert viewCount
    EP->>FS: update recent activity
    EP->>GW: POST /notify
    GW-)Client: WebSocket broadcast
